text: Combine the following statements into a well-knit paragraph: The King of the Goths no longer dissembled his appetite for plunder and revenge—he appeared in arms under the walls of the capital—the trembling senate had no hope of relief—they prepared a desperate resistance—they wished to delay the ruin of their country—they were unable to guard against the secret conspiracy of slaves and domestics—these were attached to the cause of the enemy—at midnight the Salarian gate was silently opened—the inhabitants were awakened by the tremendous sound of the Gothic trumpet—the Imperial City was delivered to the licentious fury of the tribes of Germany and Scythia.
